tellraw @s[tag=swPool_EN] [{"text":"➇ Use manual force control to set the power of the next shot (instead of being determined by charge time). Select a <> button from the first row to set force in 10% increments, and a <> button from the second row to fine-tune in 1% increments. The two values are combined to determine the final shot power as a percentage of maximum charge. Select <cancel> to revert to normal charge behavior.","color":"white"}]
tellraw @s[tag=swPool_CN] [{"text":"➇ 使用手动力度控制来设定下一杆的击球力度（而不是由蓄力时间决定）。第一行按钮用于设置10%为单位的力度，第二行按钮用于设置1%为单位的微调，二者叠加得到最终的击球力度（相对于最大蓄力的百分比）。点击<取消>会恢复默认蓄力机制。","color":"white"}]
